Tips for OR:
- Use OR when only one of several conditions needs to be true.
- Use parentheses when combining OR with AND.
- Use IN as a readable alternative to multiple OR conditions.
- OR can be used with text, numeric, pattern, range, and multiple column conditions.
- OR is useful in SELECT, UPDATE, DELETE, and other SQL statements.

Use this file as a complete reference for the SQL OR operator with many examples.
